response.overview: The 2025 Worlds Collide is an upcoming professional wrestling event and supercard co-produced by the American promotion WWE and its Mexican subsidiary Lucha Libre AAA Worldwide (AAA). It will be the fourth Worlds Collide for WWE's developmental brand NXT and will take place on Saturday, June 7, 2025, at the Kia Forum in Inglewood, California.
response.title: WWE World Collide 2025
